WEBVTT

00:01.067 --> 00:03.348
<b> 1x26 - "Ocean Gem" </b>

00:03.559 --> 00:06.605
- I'm grounded?
- Yes, you're grounded.

00:06.606 --> 00:09.657
- You disobeyed an order.
- Now we're gonna bury you

00:09.658 --> 00:12.276
till you've learned Your lesson.

00:12.277 --> 00:13.801
That's not how grounding works!

00:13.869 --> 00:14.945
Dad?

00:14.946 --> 00:18.417
Uh, you guys better come check this out.

00:18.418 --> 00:19.440
<i>W-W-Wha?</i>

00:19.508 --> 00:22.610
<i>- Wait.
- What the ...</i>

00:22.711 --> 00:25.073
<i>- Where did it go?
- Whoa!</i>

00:25.492 --> 00:27.569
- The ocean!
- Huh?

00:27.604 --> 00:30.585
<i>Hey, it's those magical ladies!</i>

00:30.652 --> 00:34.789
- What's going on here?
- The ocean is gone, obviously.

00:34.824 --> 00:37.469
<i>That's right. Now it's just a desert.</i>

00:37.554 --> 00:41.840
<i>No one wants to take a
vacation to ... Desert City!</i>

00:41.925 --> 00:46.228
Aw, we're gonna lose
all our summer business!

00:46.262 --> 00:51.099
- And all the beach babes. Aw!
- Who's gonna buy my fries?

00:51.184 --> 00:54.937
- And my pizza!
- Who's gonna have fun at funland?

00:54.972 --> 00:58.449
<i>As mayor, I demand you
explain this immediately... !</i>

00:58.450 --> 01:00.442
It was Lapis Lazuli.

01:00.493 --> 01:04.078
- Lapis Lazuli?
- She's the gem you

01:04.113 --> 01:06.949
released from the mirror.

01:07.033 --> 01:09.034
- That's incredible.
- How did you do that?

01:09.118 --> 01:11.003
But she's a gem, just like us.

01:11.087 --> 01:14.957
<i>There's a lot you
don't know about gems, Steven.</i>

01:15.008 --> 01:18.630
<i>How could I have known the
gem contained in that mirror</i>

01:18.631 --> 01:21.997
- would Be so powerful?
- Where are you going, Steven?

01:22.065 --> 01:24.633
I'm leaving to
fix what I did to our home.

01:24.701 --> 01:27.202
I was the one who set
Lapis free from the mirror.

01:27.270 --> 01:29.204
<i>Now it's my fault the ocean's gone.</i>

01:29.272 --> 01:33.475
I'm gonna bring the ocean back
or get really thirsty trying.

01:33.543 --> 01:36.311
Wait up, kiddo.
I'm coming with you.

01:36.379 --> 01:40.315
I want to help, too.
Also, I feel weird being in your

01:40.383 --> 01:43.051
house if you're not here.

01:44.988 --> 01:47.393
Clearly, we're coming, too.

01:47.428 --> 01:48.957
You're
ungrounded, by the way.

01:49.025 --> 01:52.227
Whoo-hoo!
Road trip!

